    "description": "Do you want to know if you are a good tomb raider? <strong>Dungeon Danger Traps</strong> will help you find out! And it will also allow you to prove everyone that you are also a first-class runner! But be careful, who knows where the road will lead if you choose the wrong path.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leaderboards</h2></strong><br>Each race is reflected in the leaderboard and this will serve as proof of your skill!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Different ways to complete the levels</h2></strong><br>At the levels, you will meet forks, so you will have to choose which path is the best to get ahead of your rivals!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1699740/extras/4e9a1d3c2b684a73a896a5ad7f7b353a.poster.avif?t=1717061648\" width=476 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1699740/extras/4e9a1d3c2b684a73a896a5ad7f7b353a.webm?t=1717061648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1699740/extras/4e9a1d3c2b684a73a896a5ad7f7b353a.mp4?t=1717061648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Traps</h2></strong><br>Each level is fraught with treacherous obstacles, such as stakes, darts, sliding walls and much more!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Updates</h2></strong><br>There is not a single failed level left without a record set? It doesn't matter! The levels will be constantly refilled thanks to regular updates!",
